    <item>
      <title>[주말의 가족 영화] (6) 할리우드 영화 ‘위키드’</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/weekend/2025/02/08/TBPGFYNIMBCLDFT3L2KOGF7GXU/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/weekend/2025/02/08/TBPGFYNIMBCLDFT3L2KOGF7GXU/</guid>
      <dc:creator>김양수 만화가 muplie@naver.com</dc:creator>
      <description/>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 15:30:00 +0000</pubDate>
